Purpose
-------
This repository is provided to facilitate private evaluation, academic review,
non-commercial research, and reproducible testing of Enchan CLI and its related
local runtime integration.

Definitions
-----------
"Materials" means all contents of this repository, including but not limited to:
source code, scripts, text, configuration files, installer scripts, command-line
interfaces, runtime integration code, documentation, and any other files.

"Non-Commercial" means not primarily intended for or directed toward commercial
advantage or monetary compensation.

"Evaluation Use" means installing, running, inspecting, and testing the Materials
to evaluate Enchan CLI behavior, reproduce diagnostics, or review the implementation.

